Class Rule

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.adamcin.oakpal.api.Rule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JsonObjectConvertible

    @ProviderType
public class Rule
extends Object
implements JsonObjectConvertible
    Standard Rule tuple capturing a rule type (include/exclude or allow/deny) and a regex pattern.

    config options:

    type
    The RuleType of the rule: include or exclude (or allow or deny). The meaning of this value is usually dependent on context.
    pattern
    A regular expression pattern matched against the full context value (start [^] and end [$] are assumed).
